text = "“I need not to be afraid of the void. 
The void is part of my person.
 I need to enter consciously into it. 
To try to escape from it is to try to live a lie. 
It is also to cease to be. 
My acceptance of despair and 
emptiness constitutes my being; 
to have the courage to accept 
despair is to be.” - Micheal Novak







Developed by: Muhammad Osaid Hassan
Story by: Muhammad Osaid Hassan
Designed by: Abdul Hadi Malik


"
